{"tid":2030893,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講本身輸緊50比0, 國安法反而打開缺口","createTime":"2020-05-23T05:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T11:27:30.000Z","uid":56546,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ec96339fcaf8410dc0a5ca56ad1e743f97812dbe","tid":2030893,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"其實只要中共乜柒嘢都唔做, 香港人根本無辦法維持每星期嘅遊行同攬炒行為<br />\n黑警只要keep 住每日清算手足, 打散真香港人本身只係時間問題<br />\n而外國亦都好難有咩理由插手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但今次中共咁樣出招, 有份係香港攞着數嘅國家根本好難唔再行動<br />\n<br />\n其實諗深一層大家仲有咩可以輸？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不論結果係點<br />\n今次攬炒必定會發生<br />\n不過可唔可以重生真係靠大家"},{"pid":"0ccaba09a2392bcaea47a77bcea7e0ff4978276f","tid":2030893,"uid":167467,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:09:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 反抗</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 建國</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"648d3bbc5777045ad58ecd001981a0f837f6d72d","tid":2030893,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d0e3ec103a18e677d9e633e1e1bd284b6a2983","tid":2030893,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:15:01.000Z","msg":"agger， 乘勝追擊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"},{"pid":"ca5ffc86e2673f91d9bfaa44738d924ff45f1175","tid":2030893,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4ba2bdc4b16e9040ed794a656a6e6db6fbab00","tid":2030893,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:19:20.000Z","msg":"不嬲無輸<br />\n輸點會出國安法呢啲大招"},{"pid":"817f193af453152c25ba94c629a9579616aa39a7","tid":2030893,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b4ba2bdc4b16e9040ed794a656a6e6db6fbab00","tid":2030893,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:19:20.000Z","msg":"不嬲無輸<br />\n輸點會出國安法呢啲大招"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"最怕國安法都未係大絕"},{"pid":"57f78bbb3a7347c501c59b184af3c165d5a3d33a","tid":2030893,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec96339fcaf8410dc0a5ca56ad1e743f97812dbe","tid":2030893,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"其實只要中共乜柒嘢都唔做, 香港人根本無辦法維持每星期嘅遊行同攬炒行為<br />\n黑警只要keep 住每日清算手足, 打散真香港人本身只係時間問題<br />\n而外國亦都好難有咩理由插手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但今次中共咁樣出招, 有份係香港攞着數嘅國家根本好難唔再行動<br />\n<br />\n其實諗深一層大家仲有咩可以輸？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不論結果係點<br />\n今次攬炒必定會發生<br />\n不過可唔可以重生真係靠大家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c1156f6dec30656be3f3341aa4b041a7ed249a","tid":2030893,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"小學畢業係咁"},{"pid":"9439700beee1f10d8cdccb82a7ceba9f38073a75","tid":2030893,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"817f1